18.description:
La distancia y el tiempo son siempre un obstáculo que dificulta que dos personas lleven una relación, por esto mismo a veces no pueden transmitir sus sentimientos, compartir momentos y disfrutar de ellos. 

Es por eso que a través de Fifui, les brindaremos a ti y a esa persona especial en tu vida (ya sean pareja, novios o mejores amigos), un espacio íntimo para compartir, donde podrán expresarse de forma más segura y privada. Una relación que se vive de a dos, generalmente, necesita un espacio propio que esté lejos de miradas indiscretas.

Fifui es un servicio privado, para que sólo dos personas puedan compartir una línea de tiempo en común. El concepto detrás de Fifui es impulsar a los usuarios a  escribir menos texto y a compartir más contenido. 

Escribe tu historia con Fifui, compartiendo tu vida diaria con quien más quieras, sin importar dónde ni cuándo.

The world leading football (soccer) social media company

18.description:
HINCH.AS (pronounced "inches") is a social media hub that unites football (soccer) Players and Clubs with their Fans in a single online environment, incorporating and leveraging the large existing Facebook and Twitter fan bases for this sport. The "customers" are the Clubs and Players, who are not satisfied with what they get from existing social media networks.  

Despite significant investments of time and money in social media that have created huge audiences, Football Clubs and Players are not satisfied with the status quo.  They are frustrated because they have little control over the features and management of these social networks which operate in an uncoordinated fashion, plus they receive limited data on the users and see little financially from the opportunities they provide.  Avid football fans are also frustrated that general social networks are increasingly not the place they want to fully express their enthusiasm for the sport, which is more comfortably shared only with other fans. 

HINCH.AS is the solution for Clubs and Players, who gain control over their presence on net, and enthusiastic Fans, allowing them more interaction with each other in a focused environment tailored to their needs.

HINCH.AS Builds Universal, Exciting and Tailored Experiences for Football Players and Fans. It is:

A source of revenue for players: PLAYERS have a communication line with all football fans, not just their followers. They engage with the fans through personal and fun interactions.

A marketing tool for brands: BRANDS are seamlessly integrated into the dynamic, exposing themselves with absolute presence and actively improving the experience for the fans.

A source of entertainment and recognition for fans: FANS get to play with their idols and other fans in a fresh, football themed experience, and get recognition from their participation.
